title: Where is Ranked 5's?
body:
Me and my friends wanted to play the new season of league of legends and playing ranked 5's as a team. but we dont know how to do it/where to find it

or has it been removed?

replies.body: Gone forever. Stupid idea as dynamic includes ranked party restrictions as you can't play with bronze and diamond friends like u used to be able to do in ranked 5's....
It has been replaced by dynamic queue. Just set up a club to get your team tag and start grinding :D
